Battle of the Planets is an American adaptation of the Japanese anime series Science Ninja Team Gatchaman. Of the 105 original Gatchaman episodes, 85 were used in the Battle of the Planets adaptation, produced by Sandy Frank Entertainment. Wikipedia 
First episode: September 1, 1978
Final episode: August 1, 1985

Program creator: Tatsuo Yoshida

Adaptations: Battle of the Planets

Genres: Children's television series, Animation, Action, Science Fiction, Action/Adventure, Adventure Film
